race.comment: THE DAILY PLANET (15) was a winner here three back when he stormed home from well back to score. Has raced in two richer races since. Back in grade and Meech back aboard. Will give a start but looks hard to hold out. HANDY FRIEND (5) has been freshened since storming home to finish runner-up here last time. Both recent runs have been here and is close to a win. Hard to hold out. SHE'S IMPECCABLE (10) ran fifth behind THE DAILY PLANET two back then charged home for third latest. Another close to a win. WILD WILLY (2) has been racing well including a last start win in similar grade over the border. Worth following up.
